---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 505
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Trust in God
  - 618
By: Ibn 'Atâ’illâh
---
When He gives to thee He has thee witness His Benevolence, and when He
denies thee He has thee witness His Constraint; and in either case He
is acquainting thee with Himself and approaching thee by means of His
Kindness.
